76561198043222323,Recommended,242760,24238250,"Posted: 10 July, 2016",all,CetoMatu,A fun thrilling game that I would recommend. The cannibals and mutations really give off a eerie feeling when you encounter them which gives off a strong sense of survival and danger and most importantly vulnerability. You usually cannot just attack a group of enemies without facing dire consequences you have to make the right decisions to stay prepared with items and bring stability to your base.There are some story elements to the game which are not fully completed but the devlopers are updating pretty steadily and so you may eventually have some sort of goal within the game if survival is not enough for you.The building is also fun. You can fairly large structures if you have the resources for it (takes a long time to gather wood and stone) although there is no grid feature to keep buildings and structures aligned and even so you will have to use your eye or some carefull aligning to build something accurately.Overall I recommend the game as there are features yet to come and it is an enjoyable experience werether with friends or alone.
