 so that each player has to press a key within 5 seconds so that they can all fall asleep simultaneously and wake up at the same time.-When I host a game, I see a wild boar, but the other player sees a deer. This doesn't break the game, but it's quite a funny bug.-Knives. It's almost weird that they're not included in the game. They could be used to improve and/or upgrade tools and also as a weapon.-We aren't 100% certain of this, but we're pretty sure the cannibal/mutants seem to be less frequent and perhaps ""dumbed down"" in coop?- Rechargeable Crank flashlight?I am aware that the game is still in Early Access, but I will mention this: The developers are listening to the community and are actively working on the game. They have a very detailed list of their fixes on their website and I will say with confidence that this is probably the best early access title I've played, especially for the price that it's selling for."
