y set a timer for when the next update gets out, and they're making progress.All in all, if you're hesitate because of the horror part, make sure you have a friend to play with, and it becomes epic. Otherwise, what's $15 stopping you from buying this masterpeice?It has a lot of bugs, but is still a ton of fun despite that."
