aring logs, to name one), but it's a very enjoyable experience nonetheless.I just bought this game during the sale, but that doesn't mean it's not worth the $14.99. Unlike most early access titles, the devs pay attention to what needs to be done.*** NON SPOILER SECTION ***tl;drGraphics, Audio, Gameplay, basically everything about this game is great. When you experience ""El Forest,"" you will see the work that was put into this masterpiece."
