 could just save the game instantly by going into the Menue and even create a pause while doing so, you would make the game a lot more comfortable for all players.These are my 3 Points and i hope the Developers get to read them.Number 2 is my minor Problem since i really found my addiction to this game but in an unplayable state.Despite these rather negative Aspects which shall be fixed soon, this game provided me an uncomparable experience and i'm looking forward on playing it again once the minor bugs are gone. I recommend it.Greetings"
