76561198066626944,Recommended,242760,16724478,"Posted: 26 June, 2015",all,Ropp,"Considering buying this? Well, here's why I think you should.The Forest is an Open World survival game where It's You vs Cannibals & Nature. You must scavenge for food, water, and supplies. Gather as much wood, sticks, rocks, and anything else you can find before night comes. During the night your primary goal is to survive the waves of cannibals, without dying. Pretty simple objectives. You can choose to play online, join forces with your friends (or strangers), and build massive bases and fight off the waves of cannibals. Or you can choose to play solo and face all the challenges alone, which in my eyes, is alot harder & more challenging. Playing with online is an amazing feature because It alows you and your friends to co-op and try to survive together. You guys can discuss base plans and survival tactics, and you can fight along side them, making you a virtually impossible team to stop. It's awesome, I recommend playing with friends HIGHLY. Also, I've met some great friends just by joining random servers, which is also where you can get some great help. Building is completely custom. You can build anything, anywhere.The Graphics are great, the world is absolutely beautiful, and the goal is plain and simple: Survive.With all this being said, the game is only gonna get better, considering that it is still in early alpha. So if you aren't Intrigued yet, then I don't know what else will work.Graphics 9/10Gameplay: 10/10AI: 7/10Online: 9/10OVERALL: 9/10I hope this has helped your decision!"
