 food.Night 6: Huddled in my cabin. Windows were a bad idea. The hills are alive... With screaming.Day 7: Found five dead bodies outside my cabin. I may have picked a bad location.Day 8: Made a bow and hunted some deer. Also finished a rabbit cage and trap. Lizard jerky and mushrooms for lunch. Build a little bench next to my pond. Gonna work on some defensive walls tomorrow.Night 8: More fighting. I think they want my lizard jerky...Day 9: Stayed inside. Golum is sitting on my bench.Day 10: Golum is still sitting on my bench...Day 11: Shot Golum in the face with my bow. He never moved. He may have already been dead. Made pretty art out of him and lit it on fire.Day 12: The locals don't like my art. They put up some of their own. I tore it down and put up more of my art.Day 13: There are forest people in my camp. I really need to find a new place to live.Day 14: Found a new place to live. And I'll have some nice neighbors.Daight ??: Woke up in a cave. The villagers tried to nom my face. But it's okay. I still have my lighter.Dighy ??: SQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUIDSQUAARRRGGGHHHhhh...11/10 Will get revenge on the squid-babies."
