u at any moment is great. Also to the fact that The Developers can actually make them flank me and make me extremely horrified to find out if i survive...quite the bit of suspense. The game may need work, and i gotta say, it does. Its STILL is an amazing survival game. I can barely call this a survival horror when they are always around (I mean Jerry). The devs did top notch on everything, the mutants are unlike anything that i have ever seen before, and the means of building a home, i bet if i actually tried to make some of these (apart from effigies) i could get pretty far in making these actually stand and work.if i had to grade this game... B+ its very good, and i hope to see more updates. And if co-op ever comes out for this games guys...DONT TREAT IT LIKE DAYZ.... that is all87/100 WOULD PLAY ALL DAY, EVERY DAY"
